---

<BaseLayout
  title="Promotor STIFIn - Program Licensed Promotor"
  description="Program Licensed Promotor STIFIn: peluang profesi fleksibel, berdampak, dan didampingi dari awal sampai siap melayani klien."
  schemaType="Organization"
>
  <!-- Hook -->
  <section
    class="relative overflow-hidden text-white"
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d5f4e 0%, #05291f 100%);"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0"
        style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=%2760%27 height=%2760%27 viewBox=%270 0 60 60%27 xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%3E%3Cg fill=%27none%27 fill-rule=%27evenodd%27%3E%3Cg fill=%27%23ffffff%27 fill-opacity=%270.05%27%3E%3Cpath d=%27M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z%27/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"
      ></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-24 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center mb-5 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-white/35 bg-white/10 text-sm font-semibold shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm">
            Peluang Karier dan Dampak Sosial
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-5 leading-tight">
            Pendaftaran Licensed Promotor STIFIn: Penghasilan Naik, Waktu Tetap Fleksibel
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-primary-100 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Untuk profesional, pengusaha, pendidik, dan siapa pun yang ingin punya profesi berdampak sambil membangun income yang lebih terarah.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mb-6">
            <a
              href="#offer-program"
              style="background-color:#facc15; color:#111827; border-color:#facc15;"
              class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full border-2 font-bold text-lg leading-none transition-all shadow-lg"
            >
              Lihat Penawaran
            </a>
            <a
              href="#cta-promotor-stifin"
              class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center bg-white text-primary-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-full border-2 border-white font-bold text-lg leading-none hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all shadow-lg"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
              </svg>
              Konsultasi
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
            <p class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span>&#9989;</span><span>Potensi penghasilan lebih dari 3x UMR DKI Jakarta</span></p>
            <p class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span>&#9989;</span><span>Sistem dan mentoring berjalan nasional</span></p>
            <p class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span>&#9989;</span><span>Cocok untuk yang ingin fleksibilitas kerja</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/20 shadow-2xl bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <img
              src="/hero-stifin.png"
              alt="Licensed Promotor STIFIn sedang melayani klien"
              width="1600"
              height="893"
              loading="eager"
              decoding="async"
              fetchpriority="high"
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 via-teal-600 to-cyan-600">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-white text-center">
        PENDAFTARAN LICENSED PROMOTOR STIFIn DIBUKA
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-primary-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
          <span class="inline-block bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            PAS - Problem
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-4">
            Banyak Orang Ingin Naik Level Income, Tapi Masih Terkunci di Pola Lama
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Ingin profesi lebih fleksibel dan bernilai, tapi belum menemukan model kerja yang jelas, terbukti, dan bisa langsung dijalankan.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-4">1</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Penghasilan Mentok</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Kenaikan income lambat dan sering tidak sebanding dengan energi yang dikeluarkan.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-4">2</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Waktu Tidak Fleksibel</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Rutinitas kerja kaku membuat sulit menata prioritas antara pekerjaan, keluarga, dan pengembangan diri.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-4">3</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Belum Punya Sistem</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Ingin mulai layanan konsultatif, tetapi belum punya metode, lisensi, dan pendampingan yang terstruktur.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Agitate -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-secondary-50 text-secondary-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            PAS - Agitate
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">
            Jika Ditunda Terus, Yang Hilang Bukan Hanya Penghasilan
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Anda juga kehilangan momentum membangun positioning profesional, jaringan klien, dan karier bermakna yang bisa bertumbuh jangka panjang.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-secondary-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-800 font-semibold mb-3">Dampak yang sering terjadi:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-red-600 mt-1">x</span><span>Potensi besar tidak terpakai maksimal</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-red-600 mt-1">x</span><span>Peluang klien terlewat karena belum siap melayani</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-red-600 mt-1">x</span><span>Waktu habis untuk aktivitas tanpa leverage</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Karier Sulit Naik Kelas</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Tanpa lisensi dan metode jelas, membangun kredibilitas jadi lebih berat.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Impact Sosial Tertunda</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Banyak orang membutuhkan pemetaan potensi, tetapi belum mendapat edukasi yang benar.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Burnout Lebih Mudah Terjadi</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Saat kerja tidak selaras dengan potensi, energi cepat habis dan hasil terasa stagnan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="inline-block bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            PAS - Solution
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-4">
            Licensed Promotor STIFIn: Solusi Praktis untuk Income dan Impact
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            Anda tidak memulai dari nol. Ada metode, lisensi, tools, dan pendampingan agar bisa bertumbuh lebih cepat dan lebih terarah.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Apa Itu STIFIn?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              STIFIn adalah pemetaan mesin kecerdasan dominan berbasis biometrik sidik jari dengan akurasi tinggi untuk membantu seseorang hidup lebih selaras dengan potensi alami.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">5 mesin kecerdasan utama:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">S</span><span>Sensing</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">T</span><span>Thinking</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">I</span><span>Intuiting</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">F</span><span>Feeling</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2"><span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">In</span><span>Insting</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Mengapa Menjadi Licensed Promotor STIFIn?</h3>
            <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 list-decimal pl-5">
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Potensi Penghasilan Tinggi:</span> peluang income lebih dari 3x UMR DKI Jakarta.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Fleksibilitas Tinggi:</span> tidak terikat waktu dan tempat.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pendampingan dan Mentoring:</span> dibina sampai siap jalan.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Support Marketing Kit:</span> materi promosi siap pakai.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Bermanfaat Bagi Banyak Orang:</span> membantu orang menemukan jalurnya.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Tes Simpel dan Akurat:</span> proses praktis dengan biometrik.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Market Potensial:</span> minat terhadap STIFIn terus bertumbuh.</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">Tahapan Menjadi Licensed Promotor STIFIn</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary-100">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-4">1</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Workshop STIFIn Level 1 (WSL1)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Ikuti Workshop STIFIn Level 1 selama 1 hari untuk memahami konsep dasar STIFIn, 9 personality genetik, dan sirkulasi mesin kecerdasan.</p>
              <div class="mb-3 rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 py-3 pr-3 pl-5">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wide text-amber-700 mb-1">HARGA WSL1</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Normal: <span class="line-through text-red-600">Rp 1.500.000</span></p>
                <p class="text-xl font-extrabold text-emerald-700 leading-tight">Promo: Rp 990.000</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mt-1">Hemat Rp 510.000</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Materi Workshop Level 1:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span><span>Mesin kecerdasan &amp; personality genetik</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span><span>Sirkulasi STIFIn &amp; Golden Rule STIFIn</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span><span>Ujian WSL1 &amp; sertifikat elektronik</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-secondary-100">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-4">2</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Workshop STIFIn Level 2 (WSL2)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Lanjutkan ke Workshop STIFIn Level 2 selama 2-3 hari untuk memperdalam materi, praktik analisis hasil tes, dan lulus ujian kompetensi.</p>
              <div class="mb-3 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 py-3 pr-3 pl-5">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wide text-emerald-700 mb-1">HARGA WSL2</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Normal: <span class="line-through text-red-600">Rp 6.000.000</span></p>
                <p class="text-xl font-extrabold text-emerald-700 leading-tight">Promo: Rp 4.990.000</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mt-1">Hemat Rp 1.010.000</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Materi Workshop Level 2:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-700 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span><span>Konsep STIFIn level advance</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-700 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span><span>Praktik langsung analisis hasil tes</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-700 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span><span>Ujian kompetensi Licensed Promotor</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary-100">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-4">3</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Dapatkan ID Aplikasi &amp; Instalasi</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Setelah lulus WSL2, dapatkan ID aplikasi tes STIFIn pribadi seumur hidup dan instalasi aplikasi dengan training penggunaan untuk melayani klien.</p>
              <div class="mb-3 rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 py-3 pr-3 pl-5">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wide text-amber-700 mb-1">HARGA ID &amp; SCANNER</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Normal: <span class="line-through text-red-600">Rp 5.000.000</span></p>
                <p class="text-xl font-extrabold text-emerald-700 leading-tight">Promo: Rp 3.990.000</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mt-1">Hemat Rp 1.010.000</p>
              </div>
